        <li>bnf_genre_intro->A [bnf_genre] session preserved on a worn cartridge.</li>
        <li>bnf_genre_intro->An archive of [bnf_genre] committed to microtape storage.</li>
        <li>bnf_genre_intro->Recovered [bnf_genre] material pressed into a fragile cartridge.</li>

        <!-- Genres (no pipes; includes Western bebop) -->
